{# Hero Section #}
<div class="reservations-hero" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(122, 139, 111, 0.12) 0%, rgba(139, 111, 71, 0.12) 100%); padding: 4rem 2rem; text-align: center; border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3);">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem); color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            Host Your Special Event
        </h1>
        <p style="font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2.5vw, 1.4rem); color: var(--warm-brown); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Create magical memories in our enchanting bookstore space, perfect for birthday parties, tea parties, baby showers, and other celebrations.
        </p>
        <a href="#inquiry-form" class="cta-button" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--aged-gold), var(--muted-gold)); color: white; padding: 1rem 2.5rem; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; border: none; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3);">
            Get Started
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
    {# About the Space Section #}
    <section style="max-width: 900px; margin: 4rem auto;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--deep-brown); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
            Our Event Space
        </h2>

        <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 3rem; border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3);">
            <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--dark-text); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                The Wandering Lantern offers a warm, literary atmosphere that brings a unique charm to any celebration.
                Our thoughtfully curated space provides the perfect backdrop for creating lasting memories with family and friends.
            </p>

            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted-gold); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">
                Our event space is new and evolving — photos coming soon as we host our first celebrations!
            </p>

            {# Space Details Grid #}
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
                <div>
                    <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--aged-gold); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                        Capacity
                    </h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.6;">
                        Comfortable for about 30 seated guests, or up to 50 for events with a mix of seating and standing. Final capacity depends on layout and activities.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--aged-gold); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                        Availability
                    </h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.6;">
                        Always private during non-business hours. During store hours, we offer semi-private events separated from the shop with elegant curtains, or fully private with a store buyout.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--aged-gold); margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
                        Duration
                    </h3>
                    <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.6;">
                        Events are typically booked in 2-hour blocks, with the option to extend for larger groups or events that need more time.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    {# Event Packages Section #}
    <section style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 4rem auto;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--deep-brown); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            Event Space Packages
        </h2>
        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--warm-brown); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 3rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Choose the package that fits your celebration, from just a private gathering to a fully hosted experience.
        </p>

        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
            {# Basic Gathering Package #}
            <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--aged-gold); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; text-align: center;">
                    The Secret Garden
                </h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted-gold); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                    Space (+ story if desired)
                </p>
                <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-grow: 1;">
                    A flexible, private use of our event space for your group to gather and celebrate. Includes access to tables and chairs, with the option to use our existing cozy furniture or arrange the room to fit your needs. You're welcome to bring your own food, cake, decorations, and activities, and handle setup and cleanup.
                </p>
                <div style="background: var(--parchment); padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: auto;">
                    <p style="color: var(--warm-brown); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                        <strong style="color: var(--deep-brown);">Optional:</strong> Staff-led story time may be added at no cost when available.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            {# Story + Creative Experience Package #}
            <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 3px solid var(--aged-gold); display: flex; flex-direction: column; position: relative;">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.75rem; color: var(--aged-gold); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
                    Mad Hatter's Tea&nbsp;Party
                </h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted-gold); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                    Story + Activity
                </p>
                <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-grow: 1;">
                    Everything in the Basic Gathering, plus a guided story time and a simple creative activity. This option is great for groups looking for a little structure and engagement, without needing to plan every detail themselves. Craft activities are designed to be approachable and age-appropriate, with details discussed ahead of time based on group size and needs.
                </p>
            </div>

            {# Full Hosted Celebration Package #}
            <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--aged-gold); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; text-align: center;">
                    The Royal Ball
                </h3>
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted-gold); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-style: italic;">
                    Fully Hosted
                </p>
                <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; flex-grow: 1;">
                    Our most complete option. Includes private use of the space, guided story time, a facilitated craft activity, light snacks, and full setup and cleanup handled by our team. This is a relaxed, turnkey experience where families can show up, enjoy the moment, and leave the details to us.
                </p>
                <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(122, 139, 111, 0.12) 0%, rgba(139, 111, 71, 0.12) 100%); padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--aged-gold); margin-top: auto;">
                    <p style="color: var(--deep-brown); margin: 0; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; line-height: 1.6;">
                        Perfect for a stress-free celebration
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--warm-brown); max-width: 800px; margin: 3rem auto 0; line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic;">
            All events are scheduled based on availability and group size. Pricing varies by package and timing, and we're happy to help you choose the best fit.
        </p>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
            <a href="#inquiry-form" class="cta-button" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--aged-gold), var(--muted-gold)); color: white; padding: 1rem 2.5rem; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; border: none;">
                Book Your Event
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    {# Perfect For Section #}
    <section style="max-width: 900px; margin: 4rem auto; text-align: center;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
            Perfect For
        </h2>

        <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--warm-brown); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            We welcome both children's celebrations and adult gatherings in our literary space.
        </p>

        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 1.5rem;">
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--aged-gold), var(--muted-gold)); color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;">
                Birthday Parties
            </div>
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--aged-gold), var(--muted-gold)); color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;">
                Baby Showers
            </div>
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--aged-gold), var(--muted-gold)); color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;">
                Book Clubs
            </div>
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--aged-gold), var(--muted-gold)); color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;">
                Family Gatherings
            </div>
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--aged-gold), var(--muted-gold)); color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;">
                Tea Parties
            </div>
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--aged-gold), var(--muted-gold)); color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;">
                Private Events
            </div>
            <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--aged-gold), var(--muted-gold)); color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600;">
                Meetings
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>

    {# Inquiry Form Section #}
    <section id="inquiry-form" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 5rem auto 4rem;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--deep-brown); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            Tell Us About Your Event
        </h2>

        <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--warm-brown); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">
            Share your event details below and we'll get back to you within 24-48 hours with availability, pricing, and guidance on which package fits best.
        </p>

        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(122, 139, 111, 0.08) 0%, rgba(139, 111, 71, 0.08) 100%); padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 2rem; border-left: 3px solid var(--aged-gold);">
            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--deep-brown); line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; font-style: italic;">
                Not sure which package is right for you? <br />That's perfectly okay — we'll help you decide after you reach out.
            </p>
        </div>

        <form
            action="https://formspree.io/f/xnjdroye"
            method="POST"
            style="background: var(--cream); padding: 2.5rem; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3);"
        >
            {# Hidden field to identify this as a rental inquiry #}
            <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Event Space Rental Inquiry - The Wandering Lantern">
            <input type="hidden" name="form_type" value="event_rental_inquiry">

            {# Contact Information #}
            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <label for="name" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    Your Name *
                </label>
                <input
                    type="text"
                    id="name"
                    name="name"
                    required
                    style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif; background: white;"
                >
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <label for="email" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    Email Address *
                </label>
                <input
                    type="email"
                    id="email"
                    name="email"
                    required
                    style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif; background: white;"
                >
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <label for="phone" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    Phone Number
                </label>
                <input
                    type="tel"
                    id="phone"
                    name="phone"
                    style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif; background: white;"
                >
            </div>

            {# Event Details #}
            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <label for="package" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    Event Package <span style="font-weight: 400; color: var(--warm-brown); font-style: italic;">(optional)</span>
                </label>
                <select
                    id="package"
                    name="package"
                    style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif; background: white;"
                >
                    <option value="">Select package...</option>
                    <option value="secret-garden">The Secret Garden (Space Only)</option>
                    <option value="mad-hatters-tea-party">Mad Hatter's Tea Party (Story + Activity)</option>
                    <option value="royal-ball">The Royal Ball (Fully Hosted)</option>
                    <option value="not-sure">Not sure yet</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <label for="event-type" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    Type of Event <span style="font-weight: 400; color: var(--warm-brown); font-style: italic;">(optional)</span>
                </label>
                <select
                    id="event-type"
                    name="event_type"
                    style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif; background: white;"
                >
                    <option value="">Select event type...</option>
                    <option value="birthday">Birthday Party</option>
                    <option value="baby-shower">Baby Shower</option>
                    <option value="book-club">Book Club</option>
                    <option value="family-gathering">Family Gathering</option>
                    <option value="tea-parties">Tea Parties</option>
                    <option value="private-events">Private Events</option>
                    <option value="other">Other</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <div>
                    <label for="preferred-date" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                        Preferred Date <span style="font-weight: 400; color: var(--warm-brown); font-style: italic;">(optional)</span>
                    </label>
                    <input
                        type="date"
                        id="preferred-date"
                        name="preferred_date"
                        style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif; background: white;"
                    >
                </div>

                <div>
                    <label for="guest-count" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                        Expected Guests <span style="font-weight: 400; color: var(--warm-brown); font-style: italic;">(optional)</span>
                    </label>
                    <input
                        type="number"
                        id="guest-count"
                        name="guest_count"
                        min="1"
                        max="50"
                        style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif; background: white;"
                    >
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <label for="duration" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    Rental Duration <span style="font-weight: 400; color: var(--warm-brown); font-style: italic;">(optional)</span>
                </label>
                <select
                    id="duration"
                    name="duration"
                    style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif; background: white;"
                >
                    <option value="">Select duration...</option>
                    <option value="2-hours">2 Hours</option>
                    <option value="4-hours">4 Hours</option>
                    <option value="other">Other (specify in message)</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                <label for="message" style="display: block; font-weight: 600; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.05rem;">
                    Additional Details
                </label>
                <textarea
                    id="message"
                    name="message"
                    rows="5"
                    placeholder="Tell us more about your event, any special requests, alternative dates, catering plans, etc."
                    style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.3); border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif; resize: vertical; background: white;"
                ></textarea>
            </div>

            {# Submit Button #}
            <button
                type="submit"
                class="cta-button"
                style="width: 100%; padding: 1rem 2rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--aged-gold), var(--muted-gold)); color: white; border: none; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s; font-family: 'Libre Baskerville', Georgia, serif;"
            >
                Submit Inquiry
            </button>

            <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 1rem; color: var(--deep-brown); text-align: center; line-height: 1.7;">
                After you submit, we'll follow up to confirm availability, walk through options, and share pricing. Final details are confirmed in your event agreement.
            </p>
        </form>
    </section>

    {# FAQ Section #}
    <section style="max-width: 900px; margin: 5rem auto 4rem;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--deep-brown); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>

        <div style="display: grid; gap: 2rem;">
            <div style="background: var(--parchment); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--warm-brown);">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    Can I bring my own food and drinks?
                </h3>
                <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.8; margin: 0;">
                    Yes! You're welcome to bring your own catering, food, and non-alcoholic beverages. We can provide recommendations for local caterers if needed.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background: var(--parchment); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--warm-brown);">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    How far in advance should I book?
                </h3>
                <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.8; margin: 0;">
                    We recommend booking at least 4-6 weeks in advance, especially for weekend dates. However, we'll do our best to accommodate last-minute requests based on availability.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background: var(--parchment); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--warm-brown);">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    Can I decorate the space?
                </h3>
                <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.8; margin: 0;">
                    Absolutely! We encourage you to personalize the space. We just ask that decorations be easy to remove and don't damage walls or bookshelves (no nails, tape that might pull paint, etc.).
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background: var(--parchment); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--warm-brown);">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    What is your cancellation policy?
                </h3>
                <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.8; margin: 0;">
                    Cancellation policies will be outlined in your rental agreement. We understand that plans change and will work with you to find a solution.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background: var(--parchment); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--warm-brown);">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    Are books available for purchase during my event?
                </h3>
                <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.8; margin: 0;">
                    Yes! We can arrange for a small selection of age-appropriate books to be available for browsing and purchase during your event - perfect for party favors or gifts.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background: var(--parchment); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--warm-brown);">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    What's included in the craft activities?
                </h3>
                <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.8; margin: 0;">
                    For our Mad Hatter's Tea Party and Royal Ball packages, craft activities are simple, age-appropriate projects designed to complement your event theme. We provide all materials and guidance. Activities are confirmed ahead of time based on your group's age range and interests.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background: var(--parchment); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--warm-brown);">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    How does pricing work?
                </h3>
                <p style="color: var(--dark-text); line-height: 1.8; margin: 0;">
                    Pricing varies based on the package you choose, group size, day of week, and time of day. When you submit an inquiry, we'll provide transparent pricing tailored to your specific event needs. There are no hidden fees.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background: var(--parchment); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--warm-brown);">
                <h3 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--deep-brown); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                    Can I visit the space before booking?
